        void gatherFiles(List<File> files,
                 KBData kbData,
                 com.lowagie.text.pdf.PdfCopyFields copy,
                 org.apache.log4j.Logger myLogger)
          throws com.lowagie.text.DocumentException,
                 IOException
        Returns a PdfReader which contains the concatenation of the the files in the order provided, with the final concatenation retrieved from salesforce.com referenced by pdfURL.
        Parameters:
        files - required list of File objects
        sfOrgID - required OrgID
        pdfURL - required URL to a PDF file from salesforce.com
        mode - optional
        aSession - required reference to the current session which must contain attributes referenced by by pdfURL
        Throws:
        com.lowagie.text.DocumentException
        IOException
